Package: StatOccu
Title: Interactive Occupancy Modeling Platform
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Manuel", "Spínola", 
           email = "manuel.spinola@una.ac.cr",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: A Shiny-based interactive platform for occupancy modeling,
    part of the StatSuite ecosystem. Includes modules for classical occupancy
    models (unmarked), with spatial occupancy (spOccupancy) and Bayesian
    frameworks (nimble/Stan) in development. Designed for teaching and
    research in ecology and biodiversity sciences.
